These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Game      | mah-jongg     | canasta |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | daisy      |
| Cigar         | bluemaster    | cain      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, orchid
There are 2 different nationalities: british, pakistani
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the british is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Transport         | motorbike      | helicopter |
| Flower   | orchid | daisy    |
| Nationality           | pakistani         | british         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: go, canasta
House: palace, colonial
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the palace house##1
2. the person playing go is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Game         | go | canasta |
| House         | colonial       | palace       |
| Color   | grey       | chestnut         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
