.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-6::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, potato
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, september
2 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit
1. the person eating potato is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |
| Food   | potato   | broccoli     |
| Birthday     | september | march    |
| Pet   | rabbit    | lizard |

