.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-20::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, airplane
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, cooking
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, water
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Transport   | subway | airplane   |
| Hobby   | cooking          | fishing   |
| Beverage         | fanta     | water |

 